  "steps": [
    {
      "title": "Isolate the absolute value",
      "content": "Divide both sides by $8$:\n$$\n|x-8|=6\n$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Find both solutions",
      "content": "The expression inside the absolute value can be $6$ or $-6$:\n$$\nx-8=6\n$$\n$$\nx=14\n$$\n$$\nx-8=-6\n$$\n$$\nx=2\n$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Add the solutions",
      "content": "$$\n14+2=16\n$$\nThe answer is <strong>C</strong>."
    }
  ]
